@node DEEPS "Deep Spawn"

@{b}Deep Spawn@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = FE(U3)
Type    = Summon Homarid (6/6)
Cost    = 5UUU
Artist  = Mark Tedin

Text(FE): Trample
          During your upkeep, take two cards from the top of your library
          and put them in your graveyard, or destroy Deep Spawn.
          <U>: Deep Spawn may not be the target of spells or effects until
          end of turn and does not untap as normal during your next untap
          phase. If Deep Spawn is untapped, tap it.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_D.guide/DSPAW}

@endnode
@node HIGHT "High Tide"

@{b}High Tide@{ub}

Color   = Blue
