@node HOMAR "Homarid"

@{b}Homarid@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = FE(C1/C1/C1/C1)
Type    = Summon Homarid (2/2)
Cost    = 2U
Artist  = Bryon Wackwitz / Heather Hudson / Mark Tedin / Quinton Hoover 

@{b}NOTE@{ub}: There are FOUR different artworks for this card.

Text(FE): Put a tide counter on Homarid when it is brought into play and
          during your upkeep. If there is one tide counter on Homarid, it
          gets -1/-1. If there are three tide counters on Homarid, it gets
          +1/+1. When there are four tide counter on Homarid, remove them
          all.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_H.guide/HOMAR}

@endnode
