@node VODMA "Vodalian Mage"

@{b}Vodalian Mage@{ub}

Color   = Blue
Rarity  = FE(C1/C1/C1)
Type    = Summon Merfolk (1/1)
Cost    = 2U
Artist  = Mark Poole / Quinton Hoover / Susan van Camp

@{b}NOTE@{ub}: There are THREE different artworks for this card.

